<p class="title">Use Case Admin</p>
<br>
<p>A user has been getting many complaints about his excessive returns of working items.  James Dean looks at his email and sees that one of the Cartridge Coders users has exceeded the site rules regarding returns.</p>
<p>He logs into the site and goes into the admin area and pulls up the users account and info.  He sets the user profile in the database so that they can no longer buy or sell on the site.</p>